`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Cause_Light
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cause light'	 <victim>

 This spell, along with Cause Serious, Cause Critical, and Harm, inflicts
damage on the victim through the careful use of applied magical pain energies.
The higher level spells, which of course use more mana, cause more damage to
the victim.

